{"tid":548940,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[ff] 有冇人可以寫隻戰鬥系統似exe嘅手機game","createTime":"2018-02-03T06:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T17:21:23.000Z","uid":54437,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45f87a4af289193489e75ac40c506d140640d18c","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"早排見到個post講洛克人exe, 令我諗返起呢隻童年回憶<br />\n<br />\nExe有好多野都好出色，劇情，人物，解謎，收集之類<br />\n但係個人最深刻都係戰鬥系統<br />\n集動作，砌deck, 砌圖/配點於一身<br />\n<br />\n到依家都未遇到另一個類似玩法嘅game <br />\n(雖然我都冇認真搵，如果有歡迎分享吓)<br />\n<br />\n跟著呢排就一路ff緊，如果將呢個系統放落手機game會點<br />\n作為一隻港豬，冇能力亦冇時間自己寫app<br />\n希望開個post分享吓自己啲idea<br />\n睇吓有冇人真係執去寫隻game<br />\n等我有生之年可以玩多次類似嘅野<br />\n<br />\n基本上冇乜時間打字同埋打得好慢<br />\n打完呢篇野，今日已經冇時間剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該會逐少post上黎<br />\n可能幾日後先會真係post到第一次野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e63899d10756d3b7c163e9fb38b7f2e63b77fcc","tid":548940,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"留名 利申我都想玩"},{"pid":"27e9373040916a74905fad67e1efa51051ffe78f","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e63899d10756d3b7c163e9fb38b7f2e63b77fcc","tid":548940,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"留名 利申我都想玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<br />\n睇吓呢兩日可唔可以post少少<br />\n無聊諗左好多野，操作同畫面配置，內容(pve/pvp), 營運模式，之類"},{"pid":"7e6e7586845e8dad174668e4fe167e524c89efc9","tid":548940,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e9373040916a74905fad67e1efa51051ffe78f","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e63899d10756d3b7c163e9fb38b7f2e63b77fcc","tid":548940,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"留名 利申我都想玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"多謝支持