:{"pid":"3382402611e6e69cdec94b2a979846c3292c96de","tid":548940,"uid":23758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"課金買晶片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T12:57:07.000Z","msg":"呢樣有諗過<br />\n<br />\n做手機game抽野就走唔甩<br />\n但係晶片我覺得大部分打返黎會好啲，我回憶中exe打怪刷晶片都係重要因素之一<br />\n<br />\n我甚至諗過部分晶片要特定條件先跌得出黎<br />\n例如一定要用劍殺隻怪，又或者另隻怪中左某種狀態先會跌之類<br />\n<br />\n要平衡有好多方法，可以整間舖頭賣稀有晶片，賣易會啲撞到稀有怪嘅道具<br />\n<br />\n又或者賣skin, 角色[有諗過除左customise(唔記得點叫，想講個砌圖) 之外, 可以直接出多幾隻角畀人揀]之類"},{"pid":"2fa2676010ba6adb1b5646425e95b9ecde1dc425","tid":548940,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"你係咩故事？<br />\n如果用exe有共嗚就要買左版權先<br />\n唔係用其他未必有人玩<br />\n維護server都要唔少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb592ae7751e5796fb629c386956a5b78de77252","tid":548940,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"你真係有興趣寫既，可以留低tg既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50873aad1fb1b51d802c49014a14087f653755ae","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa2676010ba6adb1b5646425e95b9ecde1dc425","tid":548940,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"你係咩故事？<br />\n如果用exe有共嗚就要買左版權先<br />\n唔係用其他未必有人玩<br />\n維護server都要唔少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"上面講左<br />\n我有興趣嘅係戰鬥模式，<br />\n劇情人物我覺得本身已經完得好好，再bin唔係好事<br />\n<br />\n我有諗過抄足個戰鬥模式會唔會出事<br />\n[每邊3&times;3格地圖，回合制揀&ldquo;招式&ldquo;(係唔係晶片唔重要，最緊要係可以好似tcg咁砌啲招式]<br />\n<br />\n不過神抄 抄足同平台嘅game都冇事<br />\n咁樣抄個模式應該冇事？"},{"pid":"07079950bc8ce022e23636ba4507c70da6dfc132","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb592ae7751e5796fb629c386956a5b78de77252","tid":548940,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"你真係有興趣寫既，可以留低tg既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"我真係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹係想掟啲idea出黎睇下有冇人接<br />\n資金同技術都掟唔出"},{"pid":"03481abff08582abbd091996d4f82ea0600bf881","tid":548940,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07079950bc8ce022e23636ba4507c70da6dfc132","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb592ae7751e5796fb629c386956a5b78de77252","tid":548940,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"你真係有興趣寫既，可以留低tg既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"我真係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹係想掟啲idea出黎睇下有冇人接<br />\n資金同技術都掟唔出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"小心俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f3cbe0d6e85f38355626be4246fc54e2ccaf0c","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"先講啲基本嘅<br />\n<br />\n<ins>戰鬥操作/畫面 - 1</ins><br />\n<br />\n基本上係跟足exe<br />\n打橫玩，中間偏右就係6&times;3 格地版<br />\n上面就有條&ldquo;揀晶片&quot;bar<br />\n<br />\n偏右係因為左邊要留位放一排打直嘅&ldquo;制&ldquo;，用黎出&ldquo;晶片&ldquo;同招<br />\n3粒打直應該差唔多<br />\n2排好似會唔夠位，同埋用6粒制好似會搞到太難操作<br />\n<br />\n一粒就出晶片啦，一粒普攻，一粒就其它技<br />\n<br />\n普攻方面，唔一定要跟返用洛克炮<br />\n用返其實都ok, 不過儲氣方法就要轉一轉<br />\n例如可以將粒制變成&ldquo;開關制&ldquo;，唔㩒就係連射mode, 會不停射<br />\n㩒左就會改為儲氣，儲完再㩒一下就射<br />\n至於射完係即刻變返連射mode定繼續再儲就可以再諗<br />\n<br />\n至於移動就用&quot;掃mon&quot;, 得上下左右應該唔難控制<br />\n<br />\n基本操作就得咁多，但係善用手機touch mon仲可以玩多好多野<br />\n例如出張晶片效果係 一定時間內可以瞬間移動 <br />\n即係好似啲boss咁跳黎跳去<br />\n操作方式就係㩒邊一格就跳去邊<br />\n<br />\n又可以出啲要瞄準嘅晶片<br />\n㩒邊格就打去邊咁<br />\n<br />\n(待續"},{"pid":"bf91eaf6498040e4275e405c14d5fae990ce2c91","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03481abff08582abbd091996d4f82ea0600bf881","tid":548940,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07079950bc8ce022e23636ba4507c70da6dfc132","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb592ae7751e5796fb629c386956a5b78de77252","tid":548940,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"你真係有興趣寫既，可以留低tg既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"我真係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹係想掟啲idea出黎睇下有冇人接<br />\n資金同技術都掟唔出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"小心俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"如果有人真係寫緊<br />\n驚我爆哂啲橋出黎<br />\n我可以收口<br />\n今晚搵時間開個tg等仇家易啲搵到我<br />\n<br />\n有冇份寫，會唔會變下隻pad, 有冇錢分我都唔介意<br />\n只係想玩"},{"pid":"576e630cf4086cbb3bf5f61a73c82ec2bc594d2b","tid":548940,"uid":116932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"留名十扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562bfe9f6181adede05df871d76f803eeb9485b2","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf91eaf6498040e4275e405c14d5fae990ce2c91","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03481abff08582abbd091996d4f82ea0600bf881","tid":548940,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07079950bc8ce022e23636ba4507c70da6dfc132","tid":548940,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"我真係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹係想掟啲idea出黎睇下有冇人接<br />\n資金同技術都掟唔出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"小心俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"如果有人真係寫緊<br />\n驚我爆哂啲橋出黎<br />\n我可以收口<br />\n今晚搵時間開個tg等仇家易啲搵到我<br />\n<br />\n有冇份寫，會唔會變下隻pad, 有冇錢分我都唔介意<br />\n只係想玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"開左，第一次用tg希望唔會直線自爆<br />\n@bt_up"}]}